comment: Dr. Belury is a very nice professor and really wants students to do well-- she even brought snacks to lecture for students multiple times! Her exams are almost exactly the same questions as her quizzes, so make sure to review those often. There is a weekly online quiz but otherwise exams are just quizzes and exact lecture slides. Not a bad class!
Belury is an extremely boring lecturer, however her exams are made up of exactly what is posted on the slides, so memorize these!  You do not need to attend lecture to get a good grade in this class.
